Author: Sebastian Utz <su@rtme.net>
Date:   Fri Jun 27 13:18:49 2025 +0200

    Fix the table AST parsing of group table settings to strip index prefix
    
    The `index.` prefix was not stripped for group settings like e.g.
    `index.routing.allocation.exclude.`.
    
    Fixes #18072.
    
    (cherry picked from commit fe2b6ad7429fcb7e909d2f2007b1b0ed66814322)

